import React from 'react'
import Button from 'react-bootstrap/Button';
import Form from 'react-bootstrap/Form';
import { Card } from 'react-bootstrap';

const LoginAdmin = () => {
  return (
    <Form>
        <Card style={{ width: "18rem" }}>
